snippet.title: NEIGHBORS: Suburban Warfare - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to NEIGHBORS: Suburban Warfare! A lighthearted, team-based PvP game about neighborhood warfare! Deploy traps and barricades to defend your own house.  Use items that only go crazier over time to get the better of your Neighbors!

Wishlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1732430
Join our Discord: https://discord.gg/invisiblewalls
